description:
&lt;p&gt;Bedford Psychiatric Liaison service are recruiting!!&lt;br /&gt;A service constantly growing and developing that provides care to those people that enter the doors of a very busy hospital. This is an opportunity for those nurses who want to further develop their assessment skills and gain experience working as part of a friendly and experienced team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The team responds to referrals form the emergency departments and the hospital wards and responds quickly to support our colleagues with all mental health concerns,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The team works over a 24hr 7 day roster with a share of both days and nights. &lt;br /&gt;We are seeking nurses with at least 2 years post qualification experience and that have the interests of patient experience and positive outcomes as a core value to their practice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please in your application provide three reasons why you should be shortlisted for this exciting opportunity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
